4.Applications of dbms

Banking and Finance: Transaction processing, loan management, ATM systems, financial reporting.
E-Commerce: Product catalogs, customer data, order processing, inventory management.
Telecommunications: Call data management, customer billing, network management.
Healthcare: Patient records, medical data management, appointment scheduling.
Education: Student records, course management, exam scheduling.
Government: Tax records, citizen data management, administrative databases.
Manufacturing: Inventory control, supply chain management, production tracking.
Social Media: User profiles, posts, messaging, content recommendations.
Retail: Sales data, inventory management, customer loyalty programs.
Travel and Hospitality: Booking systems, customer profiles, reservation management.

